# semanticscholar
A python library that aims to retrieve data from Semantic Scholar API<sup>1</sup>.

# How to install
```
pip install semanticscholar
```
---
<sup>1</sup>Semantic Scholar is a free academic search engine. API: https://api.semanticscholar.org/


